ORDER
PER CURIAM
AND NOW, this 11th day of October, 2016, the Application for Leave to File Original Process, the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus or Writ of Mandamus, and the Motion for Speedy Release or Relief are DISMISSED. See Commonwealth v. Cooper, 611 Pa. 437, 27 A.3d 994 (2009) (explaining that hybrid presentation is not permitted). The Prothonotary is DIRECTED to forward the filings to counsel of record.
